♪Behind them are all secrets♪

375
00:34:16,779 --> 00:34:21,074
♪Those unexpected encounters♪

376
00:34:21,707 --> 00:34:24,990
♪Are all carefully♪

377
00:34:25,772 --> 00:34:29,227
♪Arranged by me♪

