382
00:35:02,443 --> 00:35:10,232
♪I'm destined to give my all for you♪

383
00:35:10,699 --> 00:35:18,251
♪Even if my efforts may go up in smoke♪

384
00:35:18,637 --> 00:35:26,716
♪I am madly in love with you
